<h3 id="tasting-notes">Tasting Notes</h3>
<p>Bright aromas of ripe raspberry, vanilla, and coconut. Flavors of fresh and dried blackberry, pomegranate, and vanilla linger harmoniously for a smooth and luscious finish.</p>

